# m3_armor.shot — Heavy chassis with Heavy plating soaks more shots than
# the dummy. Visual sanity for the armor bar. (We can't test the dummy
# *taking* armor in this script because the dummy has ARMOR_NONE; the
# armor bar belongs to the player.)

window 1280 720
seed   4 4
out    build/shots/m3_armor
loadout Heavy "Auto-Cannon" Sidearm Heavy Standard
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

spawn_at 2240 984
mouse    1100 360

at  10 shot t010_loadout         # show full HP + armor bar
at  30 press fire
burst fire from 60 to 240 every 20
at 260 release fire

at 280 shot t280_aftermath
at 310 end
